Coffee is a beloved beverage that has a rich history dating back centuries. Its origin can be traced to the ancient coffee forests of Ethiopia, where the story of coffee began. According to legend, a goat herder named Kaldi noticed that his goats became energized and lively after consuming the berries of a certain plant. Intrigued, he tried the berries himself and experienced a similar invigorating effect. This discovery led to the cultivation and consumption of coffee, which spread throughout the Arabian Peninsula and eventually reached the rest of the world✨. 

